To implement product categorization that supports hierarchical categories and allows admin management, we need to:
1. Update the `Category` model to support parent-child relationships (hierarchical categories).
2. Implement endpoints to manage categories in the `category_controller.py`.
3. Ensure products belong to at least one category.

## Final Folder Structure:
my_project/
├── backend/
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── user_model.py
│   │   ├── password_reset_model.py
│   │   ├── product_model.py
│   │   ├── category_model.py
│   ├── views/
│   │   ├── user_view.py
│   ├── controllers/
│   │   ├── user_controller.py
│   │   ├── password_reset_controller.py
│   │   ├── profile_controller.py
│   │   ├── product_controller.py
│   │   ├── category_controller.py
├── database/
│   ├── schema.sql
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt

